title: C & C Cigars

description: Joe Chiusano from C & C Cigars stops by, and we light up the C & C Connecticut, Corojo, and L R M D cigars. Which one is the best? New cigars hitting the shelves, upcoming cigar events, and highlights from the Cigar Rights of New Hampshire Golf Tournament!
